reviews.review_text: This was my first visit to Marks,  and I was pleasantly surprised.  The staff was professional and kind and the product selection was  terrific.   I got a great pair of rubber boots at a reasonable price, and they will last for years. I would recommend Marks to everyone.

Went to look to see what kind of Rain Coats they had in stocks. I ended up getting a Windriver Rain Coat with a Hood for $120.00. It will keep me dry now when Im waking the dog in the rain. Staff was really polite and respectful. I asked her if she could cut the tags off, which she did for me. GoodcService and Friendly Staff.
Clean, neat and nice store, good place to get  work apparel at affordable prices. A young employee, help me until I get the product I was looking for.
Great service and they had exactly what I wanted.

I was at this location a few days ago & it was a very pleasant experience !!! The clerk that came to help me was very polite, knowledgeable & helped me select an excellent pair of hiking shoes. After about 10 minutes I selected one of the options she had presented me . I got a good price and excellent service. I would recommend this store!

The manager, Alex, is the most knowledgeable, understanding and helpful manager I have ever met! I have only been in Vancouver for 18 months and I have been looking for good walking shoes. I ve been to so many sports stores without any luck because the staff had other things to do??? I went to Mark s at Kingsgate Mall and Alex was so helpful and considerate of my needs. He picked out the perfect shoe and he was so personable and understanding. His customer  service is genuine. It is obvious that he is a great manager and role model for his staff because everyone who works there has the same skills!
I bought new work shoes and insoles. I had staff that were helpful in finding what I wanted.
Impressed with the knowledge of the staff, regarding the work boots. They assisted in finding the best boot. Thank you

Found rubber boots l was looking for and a pair of jeans as well. Next visit is for a pair of nonslip work shoes. Rep was very helpful and respectful with all of my questions. Highly recommended and given 5 Stars for their support and service.
Great deals at This place on name brand products

Fantastic clothing store, with a range of work clothing and shoes / boots. Look for their specials as they often have a good selection of sale items. They also have a few non-clothing items too (water bottles, insulated bottles).

Today I had the pleasure of speaking with sales associate  Joaquin , and I am beyond pleased with his customer service. Not only did he spend plenty of time searching for a product that showed only 1 left in store, he was patient, kind, and courteous the whole time he hunted everywhere for it. We were beyond excited when his hard work paid off and he successfully found the One and Only one left in their store or any of the locations around!!! It was for our Daughters 19th Birthday and it was the only one she wanted so we can t thank you enough Joaquin! It s staff like you that make people come back and want to refer your service  well done!

I was looking for some safety shoes  then one guy reach me for helping. I was very appreciate and patiently helping customer. And also I was looking different size of shoes and he help me to make sure the other store had the other pair of shoes. I was very happy and they have great customer service.

About a month ago I purchased an expensive pair of work boots. There was a small manufacture defect and when I brought it to the attention of the store they offered a refund. Once in the store they facilitated a straight exchange no issues no worries. In and out in five minutes. Fantastic service.

I went in recently with a pair of work boots that I had purchased more than 100 days ago. The manager listened with concern to my issue and credited the amount of my boot purchase towards a new pair of boots. I was impressed by his professionalism and gesture of good will. I was also very impressed with the staff in facilitating my purchase of wonderful new work boots. Thank you all!!

Went for a Helly Hanson waterproof jacket well priced @ $120. Then theres a 25 percent off what a deal. Better than amazon. And I got the colours that I wanted. Black for my son and ox blood for me. Need all reliable basics ? Go to Marks. The online shopping only goes so far.

I just love Marks Work Wearhouse I dont go to this one very often but the staff were lovely and helpful. I tend to go to the one on 4th but all in all Marks just has the best prices and when I looking for cold-weather gear this is my go-to store and when Im looking for sweaters or even lightweight summer things I find that their sales racks never fail to please.

Hi All - exceptional customer service by the Manager Alex, and associate Phung. They quickly rectified a price match mistake and provided 25% off an item for the inconvenience - the folks here know the true meaning of customer service.

Amazing service. My dude Roger told me to come back in a couple days and hed have a pair of new work shoes in my size for me (since they were sold out), and sure enough, I now own some new shoes that are dope, exactly what I was looking for and were 30 percent off.
Great selection and fair prices.Always good to come back here. Came here to exchange my boots and didnt have my receipt. Staff was very helpful. Definitely will come back again.
Indian girl working there very helpful name Aman .She help me , The store was very busy . There were lot of customers but she help me very patiently.
Cashiers do not give good vibes and literally zero happiness but I did receive positive, quick, and friendly service from the older balding guy.

Marks is always my go to store for thermals and socks. Investing in the higher quality brands is well worth it to help keep you warm and dry all winter This location also has very friendly and helpful staff
My frist time visit to this branch. Helpful staff. One staff Helped me to find a track down a pair of boots I wanted!
Been buying the exact same sunglasses here for about 6 years. They still had them in stock. Nice.
Good variety and products also the staff is so helpful and smiling the guy at the front helped me to find best option for me.
Lots of well priced work wear
If you let them know, where you work and show proof you can automatically get minimum 20% off from work buts purchase.

Their stuff is of a good quality, well priced. Excellent sales and discounts.

the young man who assisted me was very helpful, went out of his way to find a particular item. size. really appreciated.

Great prices and selection but best of all a great layout and easy to find what one is looking for.
